# Background: LiaScript and the Dataset

## LiaScript Overview

LiaScript is an open-source authoring system that extends Markdown with interactive educational features:

- **Quizzes and Surveys:** Multiple-choice, fill-in-the-blank, matrix questions
- **Code Execution:** Executable code blocks with multiple language support
- **Text-to-Speech:** Built-in narration with customizable voices
- **Multimedia:** Video, audio, and animation integration
- **Templates:** Reusable components via `import` statements
- **Version Control:** Native Git/GitHub integration

Unlike centralized OER platforms, LiaScript courses are plain-text Markdown files hosted on GitHub or any static web server. The LiaScript interpreter (liascript.github.io) renders these files into interactive web courses without backend infrastructure.

