**Data Collection Pipeline:**
1. GitHub API search for Markdown files with LiaScript indicators
2. Heuristic filtering (75,260 candidates)
3. AI-based validation using llama3.3:70b (2,751 validated courses)
4. Metadata extraction (author, language, features, timestamps)

## Ecosystem Growth

![Cumulative development of LiaScript courses and users (2018-2025)](../figures/fig_cumulative_growth.png){width=80%}

The LiaScript ecosystem has experienced exponential growth, with 64% of all courses created in 2025 alone. This recent surge makes understanding user needs particularly urgent—development decisions made now will shape the experience for a rapidly growing user base.
